author: Rebecca Ballhaus
title: GOP Governors Implore Conservatives to Match Left’s New Energy
text:
OXON HILL, Md.—Republican governors warned conservatives on Thursday that they need to keep up with the resurgent activism from liberals, amid a wave of protests in Washington and at lawmakers’ home-state town halls.
